{"tid":1502721,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過眾籌登報叫習維尼直接回應五大訴求？","createTime":"2019-08-24T17:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:57:36.000Z","uid":196087,"like":32,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2decda37806eb69cedd295775885d5805d9112","tid":1502721,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"由六月尾開始大家都講要set deadline但一直fail，點解？因為我地冇大台！<br />\n冇代表同政府deal，set親deadline政府都可以扮睇唔到，甚至連自己人都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但 我 地 唔 需 要 大 台！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n建議再搞多次<span style=\"color: red;\">全球性登報眾籌</span>，標題直接落Letter to President Xi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內容包括：<br />\n1. 講明全港都知林鄭只係冇話事權嘅傀儡，甚至警隊建制都當佢冇到<br />\n2. 多次和平示威失敗，警方多次濫用武力鎮壓，已有七百多人被捕逾百受傷，再發展落去會變<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>翻版六四</strong></span>，所以急切要求真正有話事權嘅中央直接回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 要求習維尼喺<span style=\"color: red;\">某日（九月中？）前用指定方式（喺某平台書面回覆？）用國家主席身份回應五大訴求</span><br />\n4. 唔答應/遊花園嘅話，市民無意威脅但逼於無奈下將會用<ins><span style=\"color: blue;\">各種創意方式喜迎十月一日</span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 最後呼籲中國回復韜光養晦路線，唔好再喺國際社會無風起浪，落得被各國杯葛嘅下場，牽連香港經濟繁榮穩定，建議多關注國內民生內政問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，亦可呼籲各位世界公民用不同方式關注事件，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">twitter+ig推 #eye4hk 同 #chiNazi 兩個hashtag</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保衛世界和諧由關注香港開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將浪潮推向國際<br />\n<br />\n除咗各國登報，亦可以考慮喺網上平台（YouTube?ttv）落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當個deadline同訴求推到各世界睇到，一嚟政府同中共冇得扮睇唔到，二嚟多咗粒彈藥畀外國繼續隊維尼，最重要嘅係做到講咗好耐嘅<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">出師有名</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n出師有名好重要，宜家拖得耐啲運動好散亂，尤其係搞手之間毫無協調撞曬期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再拗參觀機場定地區鳩嗚，Set deadline先，之後自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">覺得可行嘅請幫手推+正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"20563e46a8d29cc8f69a35af21f986d82c3702da","tid":1502721,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"借位 <br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"376f45b195c257378ec11dad0bd56c82d90662b8","tid":1502721,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"241b9fbd826a09b29a166cbb62552ccf8d8f9229","tid":1502721,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T17:11:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84kYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=1ee7b246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑受干擾 無理由日推夜推連登仔完成唔到"},{"pid":"3010bfb6731cc116b6a50b05a68d366e407342cb","tid":1502721,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241b9fbd826a09b29a166cbb62552ccf8d8f9229","tid